These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, coach
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daisy
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, swisher
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, apricot
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, egyptian
1. the person who growszinnia is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the person who growszinnia is not to the left of the person who likes apricot##8
6. the japanese is not to the left of the person who likes apricot##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite      | almond-milk |
| Job          | coach      | writer       |
| Flower         | daisy | zinnia  |
| Cigar   | blend     | swisher      |
| Color   | amber       | apricot      |
| Nationality         | egyptian    | japanese       |

